  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Visit some of Slovenia's most-loved destinations on this popular multi-centre holiday</h2>
<p>Discover magnificent landscapes, dramatic scenery, and the varied flora &amp; fauna and wildlife of the Julian Alps on this multi-centre holiday which visits two of Slovenia's most-loved destinations. Spend a few days exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a> who's beauty is renowned, nestled amidst dense pine forests and surrounded by the dramatic snow-capped Julian Alps - its famous tiny wooded island has become the national symbol of Slovenia. The small picturesque village of <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a> sits at the confluence of the Sava Dolinka and Pišnica valleys against the impressive backdrop of the Julian Alps. Enjoy leisurely strolls along the rivers, or venture higher into the mountains from the Vršič Pass where the trails are rugged and the views are mighty.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,230pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Flexible durations in each destination</li>
<li>Flexible arrival and departure days</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in Bled, between destinations and from your hotel in Kranjska Gora to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
