  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Bled</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/669384e600e14e8b97ba394ba826badc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/669384e600e14e8b97ba394ba826badc}" title="Hotel Park">Hotel Park</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109547/hotel_park_lake_bled_spa_park_outdoor_terrace.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/eb0e5d83dd25482bac3c8a68c69fdfef" />Hotel Park has a fantastic location in the centre of Bled close to the lake, with everything you need in close proximity. Generous buffet-style meals ensure you're well-fuelled for any adventure, and the swimming pool and spa facilities offer space to relax, unwind and enjoy the view.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/94de03fc3b9f42eaadf51b5041aee5ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94de03fc3b9f42eaadf51b5041aee5ac}" title="Hotel Rikli Balance">Hotel Rikli Balance</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109548/hotel_rikli_balance_lake_bled_outdoor_pool_and_terrace.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/858993fbfeab4c438f2cc2b11d40f31a" />Hotel Rikli Balance is named after the famous Swiss healer Arnold Rikli and it has excellent wellness facilities, with indoor and outdoor swimming pools and the Živa wellness spa (payable locally). The hotel offers comfortable, modern, and spacious rooms, using natural materials throughout.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Bled</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Kranjska Gora</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba}" title="Hotel Kompas">Hotel Kompas</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106153/hotel_kompas_kranjska_gora_exterior.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/fc51937433504808bd2e4882609303b4" /></p>
<p>Hotel Kompas is located on the edge of the small village of Kranjska Gora, with easy access to walking trails and all the town facilities. There's a spa and wellness area with children's pool, buffet-style meals and you'll receive a warm welcome from the friendly team.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/4ed013e224da49958546ddb8415ef8af" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4ed013e224da49958546ddb8415ef8af}" title="Hotel Spik">Hotel Špik</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106154/hotel_spik_kranjska_gora_panoramic_view.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a736d3382b4a4b0fbca3a93a35b335dc" /></p>
<p>Hotel Špik is around five kilometres from Kranjska Gora, on the edge of the village of Gozd Martuljek. It has excellent facilities, with indoor swimming pools, spa and sports courts plus a children's play area. There's easy access to plenty of great walking trails and it's a nice walk along the river to Kranjska Gora.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Kranjska Gora</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
