  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Visit two of Slovenia's most-loved destinations in one holiday. Spend a few days in Lake Bled enjoying lakeside strolls, a visit to Bled Castle and the iconic Bled Island. Then travel to Kranjska Gora on the edge of the Triglav National Park where you can explore stunning hiking trails, wild meadows and the Zelenci nature reserve.</p>]]></listingDescription>
