  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you combine multiple destinations and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from panoramic walks, cultural tours and outdoor adventures to relaxing days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<h3>Visit Slovenia's most famous lake - Lake Bled </h3>
<p>For many visitors to Slovenia, Bled is a must-visit destination, with a visit to Bled Castle, the iconic Bled Island - reached by historic Pletna Boat - and a walk through the Vintgar Gorge high on agenda. Activity-seekers will have plenty to do, from the summer rollercoaster on the Straža Hill, to paddle-boarding or kayaking on the lake. Take a day trip to the wild and beautiful Lake Bohinj and walk the stunning Mostnica Gorge or take the gondola up Mount Vogel - this takes you to the best viewpoints and the start points for some really impressive hikes. Or, head to the idyllic Pokljuka Plateau to explore pretty alpine meadows strewn with traditional wooden farm buildings.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Lake Bled</a></p>
<h3>Explore Kranjska Gora and the Julian Alps</h3>
<p>Kranjska Gora is in a picture-perfect location between the forested foothills and limestone peaks of the Julian Alps, close to the Austrian and Italian borders. Walk to the triple-border point, explore the cobbled streets and pretty alpine meadows. Take a dip in Lake Jasna, ride the alpine coaster down from the top of the Vitranc chairlift, or try zip-lining at Planica. The walking around Kranjska Gora is stunning, with panoramic views at every turn - easy strolls along the river, wander the boardwalks along the wetlands at the Zelenci Nature Park, or take on a challenge amongst the most dramatic scenery in the area on a high mountain hike starting from the top of the Vršič Pass.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Kranjska Gora</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>Please note: This is an independent multi-centre holiday and you are free to choose your own itinerary in each destination. The above contains recommendations which are provided for information only and are not included in the price of your holiday. An Inghams Destination Expert will be on hand locally either in resort or by telephone and will provide advice and offer optional excursions and walking passes.</em></p>
<p><em>Special diets, including vegetarian, must be requested prior to booking.</em></p>
<p><em>The itineraries may be subject to change. Where this becomes necessary, and where practicable, we will take the steps as outlined in clause 5 of our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a>.</em></p>]]></locationDescription>
